Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.33,0:00:08.89,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kobayashi, your coffee's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.89,0:00:10.89,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.40,0:00:16.09,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna, if you don't eat quick,\N you'll be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.09,0:00:17.41,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.41,0:00:19.24,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your hot milk, Kanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.78,0:00:21.47,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Miss Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.47,0:00:22.15,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.67,0:00:25.15,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,What would you like for dinner this evening?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.15,0:00:29.54,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, well, anything works.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.54,0:00:30.74,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.79,0:00:33.24,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,No go?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.24,0:00:35.69,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything you'd like to eat, Tohru?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.69,0:00:37.24,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:40.49,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Omurice, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.49,0:00:43.22,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Nice! Let's go with that, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.85,0:00:45.73,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Make us good ones, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.08,0:00:47.28,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.28,0:00:48.72,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.18,0:00:52.94,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,When do you think you'll\N be getting home tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.94,0:00:55.97,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, I want to be home by ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.97,0:00:57.31,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.32,0:01:00.57,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Tohru, I'm heading out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.67,0:01:00.96,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'm heading out, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.96,0:01:02.94,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.19,0:01:05.31,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.72,0:01:09.55,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Time to give my best again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:43.08,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Cleaning, cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.08,0:02:44.77,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Lalala.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.77,0:02:46.87,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Beat the dust,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.87,0:02:48.14,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,crush it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.59,0:02:51.77,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,and leave no dirt or grime!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:53.13,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Wipe it out,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.22,0:02:54.73,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,wipe it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.71,0:03:01.24,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.90,0:03:07.23,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Bathroom, check!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.23,0:03:08.49,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Bedrooms, check!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.49,0:03:09.66,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Entrance, check!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:10.86,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Rooster, check!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.86,0:03:12.69,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Living room, check!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.01,0:03:17.96,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect timing on the laundry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.61,0:03:23.12,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,The weather's nice today, \Nso they should dry quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.51,0:03:25.59,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.16,0:03:27.55,Main,Delivery,0000,0000,0000,,Please stamp here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.87,0:03:31.06,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for all your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:32.81,Main,Delivery,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:38.15,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,The cushion to help with \NMiss Kobayashi's lower back pain, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.10,0:03:42.07,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the laundry's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:45.02,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is the omurice for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.53,0:03:50.29,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's all for Miss Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:52.47,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,Make us good ones, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.23,0:03:55.96,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I must prepare the best omurice ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.67,0:03:58.16,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,First, some trial runs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.28,0:04:02.67,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.29,0:04:05.69,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.69,0:04:11.13,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Fluffy, juicy eggs, hot rice with \Nketchup, all at restaurant quality!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:13.11,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,And the taste...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.51,0:04:16.65,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,is average?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.53,0:04:20.24,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that it isn't good, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.24,0:04:21.43,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:24.60,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,Make us good ones, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.06,0:04:26.65,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:31.68,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I want it to be a little more special.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.68,0:04:34.76,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Though she already warned \Nme not to add tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.55,0:04:37.66,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.97,0:04:38.87,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.27,0:04:41.58,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you, Miss Lucoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:45.02,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,I brought some snacks. Want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.02,0:04:46.87,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:51.89,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.26,0:04:55.73,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone was always saying something to me, \Nso I tried toning down the exposure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:57.02,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:04:59.56,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You should change your body next.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.56,0:05:00.34,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.66,0:05:02.64,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Please, come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.64,0:05:05.59,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.18,0:05:11.95,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder that shop receives such praise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:14.00,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put on another cup for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:16.54,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but I need to be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:18.30,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:22.89,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I was in the middle of making trial batches \Nof omurice for Miss Kobayashi to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.89,0:05:26.23,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know any techniques \Nto make them taste good?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.23,0:05:28.90,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, omurice, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.90,0:05:30.42,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:35.22,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,The quickest way would probably be \Nto use good ingredients, I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.59,0:05:36.85,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:40.10,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Later! The tea was delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.50,0:05:42.22,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,It was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:47.52,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Ingredients, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.53,0:05:49.03,sign_8333_90_Oborozuka_Shoppi,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Oborozuka Shopping District
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:54.62,sign_8465_91_Prime_Free_Range,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Prime Free-Range Chicken Thighs
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:54.62,Main-Top,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:59.15,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,If I gather good rice, \Nvegetables, and eggs...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.84,0:06:00.66,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.66,0:06:01.75,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Over budget?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.97,0:06:05.35,Main,Butcher,0000,0000,0000,,Shopping for dinner, Tohru-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.35,0:06:07.13,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mr. Tatsuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:09.59,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,This chicken is expensive, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.03,0:06:14.30,Main,Butcher,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's the best free-range \Nchicken from Akita, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.69,0:06:17.03,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Could you give me a discount?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.03,0:06:19.71,Main,Butcher,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, it's already priced as low as I can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.71,0:06:20.94,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Could you please?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:25.10,Main,Butcher,0000,0000,0000,,If I go any lower, \Nit'll hurt my own livelihood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.10,0:06:26.25,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.25,0:06:29.28,Main,Butcher,0000,0000,0000,,But I wanted to thank you \Nfor the other day, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.28,0:06:31.53,Main,Butcher,0000,0000,0000,,I could give you extra on these cuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:32.49,sign_9388_107_Chicken_Thighs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Chicken Thighs
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:33.12,sign_9411_108_Chicken_Thighs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Chicken Thighs
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.11,0:06:34.12,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,They're average!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.64,0:06:36.79,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,That would defeat the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:38.04,Main,Butcher,0000,0000,0000,,It would?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.57,0:06:41.67,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Make us good ones, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.76,0:06:44.24,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.88,0:06:56.09,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hereabouts should be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:08.64,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.77,0:07:12.60,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Kanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:19.95,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Tohru, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.95,0:07:21.90,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Ingredients for our omurice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:23.69,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,You went back again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.69,0:07:24.84,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Only for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.11,0:07:28.34,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,What eggs are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.83,0:07:31.34,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,They're Gullinkambi eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:34.24,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,The one serving as Valhalla's alarm clock?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.24,0:07:34.79,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.79,0:07:36.67,Main,Gullinkambi,0000,0000,0000,,Cock-a-doodle-doo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.67,0:07:38.35,Flashback,Einherjar,0000,0000,0000,,They're damn good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:39.70,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.70,0:07:43.10,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,An einherjar told me they're \Nincredibly delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.45,0:07:44.42,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,And this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.42,0:07:45.18,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.53,0:07:47.97,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,spring water from an elf village.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.97,0:07:50.86,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I was planning to cook the \Nrice with it. Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:56.84,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I've fought with the elves \Nbefore, so I took it in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.84,0:07:59.49,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't complain if \Nthey killed you over that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.82,0:08:04.91,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,There's also meat from bull demons, \Nand fruits that only grow in that world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.24,0:08:07.72,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,What about the rice and vegetables?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.72,0:08:10.75,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it best to use rice \Nand vegetables from this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.75,0:08:13.98,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,True, the rice in this nation is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:18.35,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently they use some magic \Ncalled "selective breeding."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:22.14,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I should have them teach me \Nthe incantation some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:23.85,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:25.76,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Time to get cooking!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.76,0:08:27.81,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna, could you help me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.81,0:08:28.52,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.77,0:08:35.28,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Roar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.27,0:08:38.92,Main,Shouta,0000,0000,0000,,Demons out! Blessings in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:39.99,Main-Top,L,0000,0000,0000,,Roar, roar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:46.40,Main-Top,L,0000,0000,0000,,Roar, roar, roar, roar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.41,0:08:44.65,Main,Shouta,0000,0000,0000,,Demons out! Blessings in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:00.38,Main,Shouta,0000,0000,0000,,Lucoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.38,0:09:01.51,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:05.13,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, were you worried about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.39,0:09:06.57,Main-Top,L,0000,0000,0000,,I-I wasn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.57,0:09:08.02,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:10.77,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:13.03,sign_13206_157_Episode_12,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 12
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:13.03,sign_13206_158_Tohru_and_Kobaya,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru and Kobayashi's Impactful Meeting!\N (We're Raising the Bar on Ourselves)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.09,0:09:16.72,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:23.30,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right, tonight's dinner is omurice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,0:09:28.07,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,If I recall, the first normal meal \Nshe cooked was omurice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.07,0:09:30.33,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's done, Miss Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.81,0:09:33.16,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,She set it out with such confidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.16,0:09:34.71,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,And it was damn good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.19,0:09:37.98,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, she always made \Nweird things, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:40.21,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking about it now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.21,0:09:46.19,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time since I had \Nsomeone willing to cook for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:51.11,sign_14083_168_Two_s_better_tha,Ad,0000,0000,0000,,Two's better than one! \NThree's better than two! \NFamily's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:51.11,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,Back then I told her it was so-so, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.76,0:09:54.44,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,Today I'll tell her...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.09,0:09:58.06,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,it's... good...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.23,0:10:01.98,Flashback,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hurry up and pass that my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.98,0:10:04.19,Flashback,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about that, \Nhurry up and fix this error!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:03.74,Flashback - Top,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you're making backups!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.99,0:10:05.44,Flashback - Top,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Help me out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.19,0:10:05.14,Flashback,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.14,0:10:06.58,Flashback,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,The deadline's almost here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:07.43,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.43,0:10:09.77,Flashback,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Kobayashi! We've got errors!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.77,0:10:10.90,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fix them at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:12.59,Flashback,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Kobayashi! Help out over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:13.33,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,Coming right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.33,0:10:14.26,Flashback,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.31,0:10:15.02,Flashback,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.20,0:10:16.47,Flashback,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.75,0:10:17.50,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:23.43,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,Another, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:24.21,Flashback,Bartender,0000,0000,0000,,Coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:27.86,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,That's my stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:28.35,sign_15054_192_Express,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Express
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.87,0:10:31.91,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I going now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:34.66,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,The mountain... sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.66,0:10:35.73,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,The air's nice here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:36.94,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! A bear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:39.86,sign_15243_197_Caution__Bears_i,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Caution! Bears in Area
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:37.67,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,Bear...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:38.49,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,Tasty bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:39.86,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:40.99,sign_15342_198__bottle,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragonslayer
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.68,0:10:46.95,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,It's pitch black!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.36,0:10:49.17,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:54.88,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:04.55,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you come from, human?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.26,0:11:16.96,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! It's a dragon! Hug me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.47,0:11:19.52,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:22.39,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Leave, you insolent human!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.39,0:11:23.53,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Or I'll eat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.49,0:11:31.89,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well, either way, I'm going to die, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.24,0:11:39.20,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,How pathetic that the last \Nbeing I meet is a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.27,0:11:40.69,Flashback - Top,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't you get tired \Nof talking that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.69,0:11:41.36,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:43.42,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,It has to wear you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.42,0:11:44.85,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:46.18,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,You need this pulled out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:48.27,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.39,0:11:50.39,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.79,0:11:56.51,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! If a human touches God's \Nsword, their mind will be torn— Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.51,0:11:57.90,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,Don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:12:02.46,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,If God exists, then... Hngh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.46,0:12:04.21,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,He should try...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.21,0:12:09.20,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,extending my deadline right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.96,0:12:06.37,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.83,0:12:13.33,sign_17547_226__bottle,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragonslayer
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.33,0:12:18.68,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we are in my dream, that's no \Nreason a dragon should be so servile.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.14,0:12:21.55,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:23.08,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yet you saved me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.44,0:12:28.08,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,I was defeated in battle with the \Ngods, and escaped to this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.08,0:12:33.01,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,I imagine you managed to remove \Nthat sword because you lack faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.01,0:12:33.98,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm truly grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:36.85,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,Who gives a damn about that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.85,0:12:37.48,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.31,0:12:39.46,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,Drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.46,0:12:40.53,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,Drink with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:44.06,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon, listen to my story!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.91,0:12:44.06,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.21,0:12:46.89,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,Drink it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.54,0:13:05.29,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.30,0:13:08.56,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,So you're a girl, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.56,0:13:10.38,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.38,0:13:13.16,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like using this spell though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:15.44,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You're a good drinker!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:18.05,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's drink \Ntogether, just us girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.27,0:13:17.94,hehehe,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,1103)}Hehehe
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.05,0:13:18.69,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Girls?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:19.19,sign_19150_246__sfx,,0000,0000,0000,,D'oh
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.18,0:13:20.53,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.53,0:13:21.55,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:24.72,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, now I'm mad! Drink! \NLet me fondle your tits!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.72,0:13:25.31,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.31,0:13:26.62,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I can?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:28.70,sign_19366_254_Several_Hours_La,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,- Several Hours Later -
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:33.79,sign_19396_255_Dragon__Slayer,Bottle,0000,0000,0000,,Dragonslayer
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.08,0:13:31.99,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,This whole world's unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.99,0:13:33.78,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'm out there working so hard, for what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.78,0:13:37.90,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, you tell them! \NLet me bring an end to it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:41.91,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,And what the hell?! Don't make me cover \Nfor your subordinate's mistakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.14,0:13:47.67,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Don't assume all dragons are those lolicons \Nwho demand a village's virgin daughters!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:53.72,sign_19963_282__bottle,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragonslayer
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.39,0:14:04.11,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I all alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.73,0:14:07.87,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Same.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.50,0:14:13.86,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all alone in this world now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:20.29,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have anywhere to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:23.96,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,No. Though I've been alone from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:25.87,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.57,0:14:28.76,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,Want to come to my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:41.43,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,I-I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:47.85,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,Then be my maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.33,0:14:48.98,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.98,0:14:52.63,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! A maid isn't just a simple servant!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:55.04,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,Normally they're divided by their \Nroles into house maids, laundry maids,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:15:00.54,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,and so forth, and it takes training to be \None, unlike those girls at maid cafés—Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.99,0:15:02.54,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.07,0:15:05.28,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.07,0:15:07.22,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,So, Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.22,0:15:09.28,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not out to deny the \Nexistence of maid cafés.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.28,0:15:10.38,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,Those are good in their own way,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:11.97,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,but they're a problem that \Nhelps contribute to the growing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:13.64,Flashback,K,0000,0000,0000,,trend of the maid profession \Nbeing taken lightly...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.66,0:15:19.43,Main,Train,0000,0000,0000,,Oborozuka. Oborozuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:26.44,sign_22056_283_Oborozuka,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Oborozuka
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.99,0:15:25.19,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I dreamt about \Nsomething important...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.83,0:15:27.85,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.85,0:15:28.76,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.76,0:15:30.93,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kobayashi, welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.29,0:15:33.34,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,We just finished the omurice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.34,0:15:34.70,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I helped, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:37.54,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm confident in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:43.04,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,The omurice was delicious,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:44.93,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,but because I had to point out so many issues,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.93,0:15:47.38,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,I again failed to tell her they were good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:01.64,Main,Taki,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it's raining all of a sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.46,0:16:03.89,Main,Taki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.89,0:16:06.72,Main,Taki,0000,0000,0000,,They said there was no chance of rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.39,0:16:13.95,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,Help me, Takiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:15.11,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,It's a guerrilla event.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.50,0:16:16.64,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,Time to grind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.23,0:16:19.54,Main,Taki,0000,0000,0000,,Coming, coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:23.61,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.61,0:16:26.25,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we'll be having\Nthis for lunch for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:28.45,Main-Top,TV,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.45,0:16:30.46,Main-Top,TV,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it okay if I pet him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.46,0:16:31.54,Main-Top,TV,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:31.88,sign_23758_305_World_Wide_Dogs,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,World {\c&H1107DE&}Wide{\c&H7D00DF&} Dogs
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:31.88,sign_23758_306_Entertainer_Spec,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Entertainer Special
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:31.88,sign_23758_307_Entertainers__Pe,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Entertainers' {\c&H009AE9&}Pet\N {\c&H8A00DB&}Gathering
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.27,0:16:33.80,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:35.45,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey, it's cramped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.45,0:16:38.05,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,What mere pets, acting \Naffectionate with humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.05,0:16:39.59,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You're one to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:40.63,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.63,0:16:41.16,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:46.81,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, were there any humans \Nyou were close to in your old world?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.81,0:16:48.02,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:55.03,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if I had to say, there was one \Nhuman I associated with for a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.31,0:16:57.46,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? What were they like?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.81,0:17:03.06,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well, allow me to talk about \Nmy former self a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:11.47,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I first met that human in \Nan empty, ruined village.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:17.51,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, guess I'll make this \Nplace my home for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.09,0:17:20.04,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:27.02,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It's rare to see a dragon \Nin a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.02,0:17:29.15,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I was just lying low for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.15,0:17:30.60,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Let me stay with you for a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.59,0:17:32.98,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,A bandit?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.98,0:17:34.45,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.45,0:17:38.49,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I mistook a noble for a merchant and \Nattacked them, now I'm on the run.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.92,0:17:41.17,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,All my comrades have been captured,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.17,0:17:44.39,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm all alone now and I\Nwas wondering what to do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:46.61,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.12,0:17:49.17,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't get lost, I'll just kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.61,0:17:52.67,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you... Why do you laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:53.93,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.43,0:17:56.21,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've \Never heard anyone say
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.21,0:17:58.53,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,they'd kill me with so little \Nintent behind the words!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.53,0:18:01.64,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Dragon, you're not used to \Nthreatening people, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:03.39,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just a threat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.26,0:18:07.55,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.51,0:18:12.46,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,So it's okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:13.81,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Let me stay for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:17.49,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Do as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:18.35,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.83,0:18:22.71,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking back on it now, \NI could've just left myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.71,0:18:27.54,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,But at the time I couldn't \Nlet myself yield to a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.91,0:18:32.78,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, what's it feel \Nlike being a dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.47,0:18:35.75,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.21,0:18:41.08,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You can fly through the sky, and possess \Nsuch power you'll never lose to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.08,0:18:45.00,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know what it feels like to \Nbe able to live freely in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.00,0:18:47.01,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You're ignoring me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.01,0:18:48.78,Flashback - Top,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.89,0:18:50.25,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,At the time I found myself thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.78,0:18:51.89,Flashback - Top,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You responded to me! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.39,0:18:52.51,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,What was my freedom like?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.51,0:18:55.88,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought of myself \Nas free before then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:19:02.55,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I was born with the chaos faction,\N lived with chaos, and fought the divine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.21,0:19:06.16,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,If that all ended, would I be free?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:07.55,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Would it ever end?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.91,0:19:11.55,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it did end,\N and I was free, what would I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.10,0:19:15.74,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,What would you do if you had freedom?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.74,0:19:16.42,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:18.21,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Be a maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.91,0:19:19.67,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,A maid?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.67,0:19:21.26,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. A maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:23.46,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'd wear a cute maid outfit,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.46,0:19:29.30,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,greet guests with my best smile, \Nfall in love with my master.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.30,0:19:31.58,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,You'd just be enslaving yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:32.30,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:34.10,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,But it'd be my choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:35.93,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I would have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.54,0:19:40.39,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,If I had a choice, I think \Nmy life would be different.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:42.57,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,If I could choose my own life,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:46.87,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,and my only two choices were becoming \Na bandit or becoming a slave, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.71,0:19:49.01,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.01,0:19:49.84,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.68,0:19:54.86,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking back on it, I had \Nnever made my own choice,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.86,0:19:57.09,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,and I thought that was fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:19:59.88,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,There wasn't anyone I wanted to see anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:04.21,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,So I chatted with that girl \Nfor a while after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:06.85,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I think I should be good now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.95,0:20:09.13,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,You're leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.13,0:20:10.14,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:13.59,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to cross the mountains and \Ntry heading to the next nation over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.05,0:20:15.87,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there'll be something there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.87,0:20:18.48,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Miss Dragon, let me ride you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:20.86,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Bug off! I'll never let a human ride me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:22.78,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Cheapskate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:25.10,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll die before I let a human ride me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.41,0:20:28.48,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Well, later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.28,0:20:32.00,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Miss Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.42,0:20:33.94,Flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.94,0:20:35.99,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,For being with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.66,0:20:38.75,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,And so I parted ways with \Nthat annoying human.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.74,0:20:41.90,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,At least, that's how I {\i1}should{\i0} have felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.90,0:20:44.92,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yet I felt a little sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.36,0:20:47.39,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,and uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.85,0:20:52.65,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe that person had something \Nto do with why you're my maid now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.65,0:20:53.64,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:58.72,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's rare of me to say this, but I \Nwouldn't mind seeing that human again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.53,0:21:00.27,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.56,0:21:01.39,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.77,0:21:03.47,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.47,0:21:04.14,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.14,0:21:07.33,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,The way you used to talk \Nsounds like an old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.33,0:21:07.75,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.75,0:21:09.43,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,But it's cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.43,0:21:10.64,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.26,0:21:14.14,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.86,0:21:17.17,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,The weather's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.01,0:21:28.76,sign_30858_407_Super_Entry_Leve,Book,0000,0000,0000,,Super Entry Level \NObject-Oriented Programming
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.01,0:21:28.76,sign_30858_408_Learn_the_skills,Book,0000,0000,0000,,Learn the skills yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.77,0:21:30.50,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.26,0:21:37.90,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,I've sure blended in to this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.99,0:21:40.81,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.00,0:23:28.01,sign_33687_414_Next_Episode,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,189)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.97,0:23:29.46,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru, do you think that \Nbandit girl is still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.46,0:23:30.96,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.96,0:23:33.31,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,But if she is alive, I bet \Nshe's serving as a maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.31,0:23:34.38,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Same as you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.38,0:23:35.65,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.65,0:23:37.40,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I hope she's getting along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.02,0:23:40.01,sign_33951_421_Episode_13,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(276,1)}Episode 13
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.02,0:23:40.01,sign_33951_422_Emperor_of_Demis,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(276,1)}Emperor of Demise Arrives! \N(It Was the Final Episode Before We Knew It)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.40,0:23:38.87,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I hope so, too.
